data.title: 1912) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Daughter of Juan Bandini and Dolores Estudillo, she married Abel Stearns at 14 years of age, he was 43.  The couple purchased the Los Alamitos Ranch near Long Beach and spent their summers there.  Stearns had his wife's name added to his investments and thus making her very wealthy.
